& [MergeDraftToPacketProposalDesign] is the design contract for converting run-local merge draft input into manual merge packet proposal evidence
  @ [draft_bridge] coordination/run_local_to_merge_packet_bridge_design.sop
  @ [manual_merge_policy] coordination/manual_merge_packet_policy.sop
  @ [draft_records] src/negotiated_agent/run_local_merge_draft.py
  @ [merge_packet_records] src/negotiated_agent/merge_packet.py
  @ [manager_job_notice] coordination/manager_job_notice.sop
  @ [created_at] 2026-05-30T01:19:00Z

  + [design_status] is ready_for_implementation_slice
  + [authority_boundary] is packet_proposal_not_workspace_application
  + [primary_goal] is convert reviewed run-local draft inputs into a ManualMergePacket proposal with explicit Manager and Shaliach acceptance refs
  + [non_goal] is target workspace mutation
  + [non_goal] is treating draft input as Manager acceptance
  + [non_goal] is treating merge eligibility as Shaliach final review
  + [non_goal] is advancing the Manager frontier

& [ProposalInputs] is what the packet proposal builder must inspect
  + [required_ref] is run_local_merge_draft_input.sop with authority_boundary draft_input_not_manual_merge_packet
  + [required_ref] is Manager acceptance record for packet proposal construction
  + [required_ref] is Shaliach review record for packet proposal construction
  + [required_ref] is run_local_execution_result.sop or source_result_ref named by the draft input
  + [required_arg] is verification command for future apply validation
  + [authority_boundary] is packet_inputs_not_apply_authorization
  = must: reject missing Manager acceptance
  = must: reject Manager acceptance statuses other than accepted_for_packet_proposal
  = must: reject Shaliach statuses that require pause, rework, or scope repair
  = must: re-check every source_ref against source_run_root
  = must: re-check every target_path against target_workspace_root

& [ManagerPacketProposalAcceptance] is the Manager evidence required before proposal construction
  + [field] is acceptance_id
  + [field] is acceptance_status
  + [field] is draft_input_ref
  + [field] is accepted_entry_count
  + [field] is frontier_at_acceptance
  + [field] is risk_summary
  + [authority_boundary] is manager_packet_acceptance_not_workspace_apply
  = must: distinguish accepted_for_packet_proposal from accepted_for_workspace_application

& [ShaliachPacketProposalReview] is the protocol counsel evidence required before proposal construction
  + [field] is review_id
  + [field] is review_status
  + [field] is draft_input_ref
  + [field] is checked_protocols
  + [field] is finding_summary
  + [field] is required_response
  + [authority_boundary] is shaliach_packet_review_not_manager_acceptance
  = must: distinguish clear_for_packet_proposal from no_scope_or_authority_blocker for final apply

& [PacketProposalOutput] is the produced artifact
  + [artifact_name] is manual_merge_packet.sop
  + [packet_form] is ManualMergePacket
  + [manager_acceptance_ref] is ManagerPacketProposalAcceptance ref
  + [shaliach_review_ref] is ShaliachPacketProposalReview ref
  + [rollback_plan] is generated from proposed target paths as pre-apply evidence
  + [verification_command] is required
  + [authority_boundary] is manual_merge_packet_not_workspace_application
  = must: never write target workspace files
  = must: never generate apply_plan.sop as part of this proposal conversion
  = must: preserve rejected output refs as empty or explicit evidence, not by deleting run-local output

& [ProofExpectations] is the minimum implementation proof for this design
  + [test_case] is accepted Manager and clear Shaliach reviews produce ManualMergePacket proposal without applying files
  + [test_case] is missing or blocked Manager acceptance rejects proposal creation
  + [test_case] is Shaliach pause or rework rejects proposal creation
  + [test_case] is source or target containment is rechecked from the draft input
  + [test_case] is packet proposal artifact preserves not-workspace-application boundary

& [ImplementationOrder] is the safe next split
  + [slice_1] is add packet proposal acceptance and Shaliach review record types plus builder helper
  + [slice_2] is add explicit CLI writer for manual_merge_packet.sop proposal creation
  + [slice_3] is refresh audit and checkpoint before connecting proposal creation to apply dry-run validation
